title: Episode 47 w/ Joe Budden
itunes:title: Episode 47 w/ Joe Budden
description:
N.O.R.E. and DJ EFN are the Drink Champs. In this episode the guys sit with MC and fellow podcaster Joe Budden. The guys discuss the incident with Taxstone, Joe's career, reality tv, Drake, podcast wars, Pettiness and a lot more. The guys are also joined by Cyn Santana and Joe's podcast co-host, Rory. --- Support this podcast: https://anchor.fm/drinkchamps/support
